// Windows application icon for exp-desktop.exe (EXP-20).
//
// Explorer, the taskbar and Alt-Tab use the lowest-numbered ICON resource as
// the executable's icon, so this must stay resource id 1. The .ico is the white
// brand logo (apps/desktop/assets/icons/logo-white.svg), matching the Linux
// AppImage's white-on-transparent choice so it reads on dark taskbars.
1 ICON "app.ico"
